tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  42,2,"God’s selected few are those who rise above traditional religion and discover the real Truth who rise above outward appearances and realise the real meaning of occurrences who recognise God’s representative and become his supporters."
  42,10,"Noah’s opponents were utterly destroyed in a terrible flood: indeed, the whole race was wiped out. The succeeding generation came into existence through those few individuals who were saved along with him in his ark."